title: The Light and Darkness War (01 - 06) (1988 - 1989) (S23Scan)
description:
The Light and Darkness War (01 - 06) (1988 - 1989) (S23Scan) 


A Vietnam vet is the only surviving member of his platoon.  Twenty years after the war is over, he survived a car crash, a coma, and now Lazarus Jones has been transported to a universe reminiscent of a Moorcock novel.  Naturally, his old platoon buddies are there, and they're fighting the forces of darkness.  There's magic, aliens, and Leonardo Da Vinci has a supporting role.
